1.title: The Oldest Mummies in the World
1.plot: Nine thousand year-old mummies have been found, not in Egypt as we would expect, but in Northern Chile. This documentary reveals the Egyptians were not the first to practice mummification.

imdb.plot outline: The historical events, people, and dramas that shaped our world. This anthology of full-length documentaries has been drawn from a variety of international sources and produced by top journalists and documentary filmmakers from around the world.
